race.comment: PRONTO ROCCO (8) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Grade 4/5 winner three back (22.56) at this track over 400m. Has the ability and can find winning form this time. PAT CARD (1) has a strong record this trip with five wins and four placings from 10 starts. Below best last time at this track (28.18) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 5.5 lengths fifth. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. YUNDERUP SUN (5) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, breaking through last time at this track over 488m. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Expected to measure up again. WEST ON ARIEL (2) drops in journey and warrants respect.
